28:38.967 --> 28:45.014
CHILDREN (SINGING):
Be it pleasures and palaces,

28:45.015 --> 28:50.062
Though we may roam,

28:50.312 --> 28:56.025
Be it ever so humble,

28:56.026 --> 29:01.733
There's no place like home.

29:01.990 --> 29:07.037
A charm from the skies

29:07.162 --> 29:12.209
Seems to hallow us there,

29:12.334 --> 29:14.835
- (SPEAKING) Father, I'll be late for school!
- You wait.

29:14.836 --> 29:18.381
You are pleased to recite proverb
you learn yesterday

29:18.423 --> 29:21.884
and writing down 12
times in copybook.

29:21.885 --> 29:23.758
"A thought for the day:

29:23.804 --> 29:25.881
East or west,

29:25.889 --> 29:28.099
home is best."

29:28.100 --> 29:31.227
"East, west, home,
best," means house!

29:31.228 --> 29:34.647
"A man's house is only less
dear to him than his honor."

29:34.648 --> 29:38.478
Every day, month after week,
something about house.

29:38.527 --> 29:41.028
Are my children to be
taught nothing more?

29:41.029 --> 29:43.072
Yesterday we are taught

29:43.115 --> 29:45.659
that the world is a round ball

29:45.701 --> 29:49.370
which spins on an invisible stick
through its middle.

29:49.371 --> 29:53.416
Everyone knows the world
rides on the back of a turtle

29:53.417 --> 29:55.376
who keeps it from
running into the stars.

29:55.377 --> 29:58.337
How can it be
that everyone knows one thing

29:58.338 --> 30:01.166
if many people believe
another thing?

30:01.466 --> 30:03.714
Then which is true?

30:05.304 --> 30:07.263
The world is ball

30:07.264 --> 30:09.057
with stick through it.

30:09.099 --> 30:10.308
I believe.

30:10.309 --> 30:11.892
You believe?

30:11.893 --> 30:14.312
Does that mean that
you do not know?

30:14.313 --> 30:17.231
But you must know,
because you are king.

30:17.232 --> 30:18.566
Good.

30:18.567 --> 30:21.441
Someday you too will be king,

30:21.486 --> 30:23.780
and you too will know everything.

30:23.947 --> 30:25.865
But how do I learn?

30:25.866 --> 30:28.114
And when do I know that
I know everything?

30:31.580 --> 30:33.748
When you are king.

30:37.210 --> 30:39.913
When you are king.

30:41.590 --> 30:43.633
But I do not know.

30:45.010 --> 30:48.384
In my head are many facts,
but I am not sure.

30:49.389 --> 30:52.593
What to tell a growing son?

30:53.518 --> 30:56.688
How to bring truth and justice
to my people?

31:01.193 --> 31:03.145
(SINGING) When I was a boy,

31:03.779 --> 31:05.697
World was better spot,

31:06.239 --> 31:08.316
What was so was so,

31:08.700 --> 31:10.527
What was not was not.

31:11.119 --> 31:13.162
Now I am a man,

31:13.538 --> 31:15.456
World have change a lot

31:15.999 --> 31:18.827
Some things nearly so,

31:20.045 --> 31:22.873
Others nearly not.

31:24.299 --> 31:27.510
There are times I almost think

31:27.511 --> 31:32.683
I am not sure of what
I absolutely know;

31:33.183 --> 31:34.975
Very often find confusion

31:34.976 --> 31:40.023
In conclusion I concluded long ago.

31:40.399 --> 31:42.274
In my head are many facts that,

31:42.275 --> 31:47.231
As a student I have
studied to procure

31:47.656 --> 31:49.657
In my head are many facts,

31:49.658 --> 31:53.283
Of which I wish I was more certain

31:53.412 --> 31:56.286
I was sure.

32:00.001 --> 32:02.545
Is a puzzlement.

32:04.589 --> 32:08.794
Shall I join with other
nations in alliance?

32:09.261 --> 32:13.091
If allies are weak
am I not best alone?

32:13.598 --> 32:17.223
If allies are strong with power
to protect me,

32:17.853 --> 32:22.524
Might they not protect
me out of all I own?

32:23.108 --> 32:26.232
Is a danger to be
trusting one another,

32:27.279 --> 32:31.109
One will seldom want to do
what other wishes;

32:31.783 --> 32:36.830
But unless someday,
Somebody trust somebody,

32:38.039 --> 32:41.914
There'll be nothing left on earth

32:42.377 --> 32:44.454
excepting fishes!

32:46.548 --> 32:48.215
There are times I almost think

32:48.216 --> 32:53.422
nobody sure of what
he absolutely know,

32:53.722 --> 32:55.431
Ev'rybody find confusion

32:55.432 --> 33:00.388
In conclusion he
concluded long ago.

33:00.729 --> 33:02.396
And it puzzle me to learn

33:02.397 --> 33:07.524
that tho' a man may be in doubt
of what he know,

33:07.777 --> 33:09.775
Very quickly will he fight,

33:09.821 --> 33:14.367
He'll fight to prove
that what he does not know

33:14.409 --> 33:15.826
is so.

33:18.705 --> 33:21.784
Ohhhh!

33:22.000 --> 33:24.623
Sometimes I think that
people going mad!

33:25.754 --> 33:28.958
Ahhhh!

33:29.007 --> 33:31.551
Sometimes I think that
people not so bad.

33:32.302 --> 33:33.969
But no matter what I think,

33:33.970 --> 33:37.515
I must go on living life.
As leader of my kingdom

33:37.516 --> 33:39.013
I must go forth,

33:39.518 --> 33:43.020
