from England.

35:29.044 --> 35:30.461
CHOWFA: I do not see Siam.

35:30.462 --> 35:32.505
The white is Siam.

35:32.881 --> 35:34.882
Siam not so small.

35:34.883 --> 35:37.632
Well, wait. Let me
show you England.

35:37.719 --> 35:40.889
