Norway is a very cold place.

41:32.156 --> 41:34.116
Sometimes it is so cold,

41:34.117 --> 41:36.243
that the lakes and rivers freeze

41:36.244 --> 41:39.573
and the water becomes so hard
that you can walk on it.

41:39.580 --> 41:41.282
Walk on water?

41:41.332 --> 41:43.079
Yes, walk on water.

41:43.084 --> 41:45.002
How is it possible?

41:45.003 --> 41:46.455
Hard water?

41:46.462 --> 41:50.465
Not only that, but the raindrops
change into small white spots

41:50.466 --> 41:52.009
that look like lace.

41:52.010 --> 41:54.463
And this is called "snow."

41:54.679 --> 41:56.096
Snow.

41:56.097 --> 41:58.140
Spots of lace!

41:58.349 --> 42:02.102
Yes, Your Highness. The water freezes
on its way down from the sky.

